    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014very well-maintained and still has that smooth, reliable feel on the road. There\u2019s a bit of character here and there from some great road trips, but overall, it\u2019s a fantastic car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
