    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused machine featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline via individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high lateral G-loads. With its communicative hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering and a well-sorted suspension geometry, this specimen offers a visceral mechanical connection often lost in modern performance vehicles.",
