      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with the paint showing only the minor, superficial character marks one would expect from a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats remain supple and free of tears, and the interior has been kept strictly smoke-free. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are in full working order. Under the hood, the car has been maintained with an open checkbook policy\u2014I have a complete folder of service records showing regular fluid changes and recent brake service. It starts reliably every morning, shifts smoothly through all gears, and sits on a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 36500.0,
