    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained over the years. The interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s just a solid, reliable car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that looks great and drives even better without the new-car price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 34500.0,
