    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system, which has been recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip M-Variable Lock differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension has been upgraded with a tuned coilover system for enhanced lateral grip and turn-in response. While the exterior shows honest signs of use, the drivetrain and chassis are dialed in for peak performance. This is a high-revving, analog machine ready for spirited driving.",
